402
00:25:21,598 --> 00:25:23,632
and go to another magazine so you won't see him.

403
00:25:23,633 --> 00:25:25,665
Live like that.

404
00:25:25,666 --> 00:25:27,366
Right.

405
00:25:28,300 --> 00:25:30,899
I should.

