419
00:26:13,666 --> 00:26:16,020
What do you mean?

420
00:26:27,833 --> 00:26:30,132
What are you doing?

421
00:26:31,499 --> 00:26:32,899
Is it true?

422
00:26:32,899 --> 00:26:35,532
That you dated and dumped Editor Na?

423
00:26:35,532 --> 00:26:37,067
