424
00:26:37,067 --> 00:26:39,466
You don't want to waste time and emotions?

425
00:26:39,466 --> 00:26:42,466
Is it true you broke up because of that ridiculous reason?

426
00:26:42,466 --> 00:26:44,065
Yes, that's right.

427
00:26:44,066 --> 00:26:44,900
So what?

428
00:26:44,901 --> 00:26:46,832
Why did you start dating her if you were going to end it like this?

429
00:26:46,833 --> 00:26:48,765
If you were going to hurt her, why date her?!

430
00:26:48,766 --> 00:26:51,531
I didn't know dating would be such a hindrance.

431
00:26:51,532 --> 00:26:53,865
You know money is the most important to me.

432
00:26:53,866 --> 00:26:55,766
Hyung.

433
00:26:55,766 --> 00:26:57,733
You're the worst.

434
00:26:58,367 --> 00:27:01,440
You're not the person I thought you were.

435
00:27:32,066 --> 00:27:33,699
When are you moving in?

436
00:27:33,699 --> 00:27:34,766
In August, two years from now.

437
00:27:34,767 --> 00:27:37,400
Two years later...

438
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:38,698
