456
00:28:40,734 --> 00:28:42,534
 Stop.

457
00:28:43,833 --> 00:28:45,532
 "Home"?

458
00:28:45,532 --> 00:28:47,700
 It's your boyfriend's... No.

459
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:50,031
 Your ex-boyfriend's home.

460
00:28:50,032 --> 00:28:52,132
Beat it.

461
00:28:52,132 --> 00:28:54,700
I can't stand the sight of you.

462
00:28:54,700 --> 00:28:56,733
 Have you given up on becoming a homeowner?

463
00:28:56,734 --> 00:28:57,799
Do you want to be poor...?

464
00:28:57,800 --> 00:28:59,165
It's me.

465
00:28:59,166 --> 00:29:03,190
I know it's me. I know I'm poor, so leave me alone!

466
00:29:04,900 --> 00:29:07,799
Don't ever appear again.

467
00:29:08,734 --> 00:29:11,499
I don't want to think about you.

468
00:29:22,599 --> 00:29:25,531
