470
00:29:27,599 --> 00:29:30,066
Write an article that can get that sold out, too.

471
00:29:30,066 --> 00:29:31,666
Yes, sir.

472
00:29:31,666 --> 00:29:35,531
Wow, how did you sell all of them?

473
00:29:35,532 --> 00:29:38,400
As expected, you really are...

474
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:40,865
He's really something for sure.

475
00:29:40,866 --> 00:29:43,666
How can he be so rude?

476
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:55,660

477
00:29:55,660 --> 00:29:59,598
