499
00:30:59,599 --> 00:31:01,399
There will be some shortcomings.

500
00:31:01,399 --> 00:31:02,467
It's okay.

501
00:31:02,467 --> 00:31:05,466
Can you tell us the floor area ratio first?

502
00:31:05,467 --> 00:31:06,733
Oh, the floor area ratio is—

503
00:31:06,734 --> 00:31:11,799
The ratio of a building's total floor area to the lot size.

504
00:31:11,799 --> 00:31:13,865
- Did you know that? 
 - Yes.

505
00:31:13,866 --> 00:31:15,700
Then the total floor area is?

506
00:31:15,700 --> 00:31:19,899
The total sum of the areas of all floors.

507
00:31:19,899 --> 00:31:22,410
I know my stuff, right?

508
00:31:26,300 --> 00:31:28,733
I guess I underestimated you.

509
00:31:28,734 --> 00:31:31,999
